headline: AUTOCANADA COMPLETES SALE OF NORTH CITY HONDA
summary: AutoCanada Inc. (TSX: ACQ), a multi-location Canadian automobile dealership group, today announced the completion of the sale of North City Honda in Chicago, Illinois. This dealership is part of the U.S. dealerships reclassified as discontinued operations at year-end 2024.
